it-Yami starrer Junooniyat is a tedious watch|website=Rediff|language=en|access-date=23 October 2019}}\n*{{Cite web|url=https://bollyspice.com/junooniyat-stupidest-love-story-decade-subhash-k-jha-review/|title=Junooniyat Is The Stupidest Love Story Of The Decade \u2013 A Subhash K Jha review|last=Jha|first=Subhash K.|date=26 June 2016|website=BollySpice.com - The latest movies, interviews in Bollywood|language=en-US|access-date=23 October 2019}}</ref> and fared similarly.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://boxofficeindia.com/movie.php?movieid=3309|title=Junooniyat - Movie - Box Office India|website=boxofficeindia.com|access-date=23 October 2019}}</ref> \n\n[[Zid (2014 film)|Zid]] received very poor reviews<ref name=\"Zid\">Reviews of ''Zid'':\n\n*{{Citation|title=Movie Zid Review 2014, Story, Trailers {{!}} Times of India|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/hindi/movie-reviews/zid/movie-review/45281125.cms|access-date=2 May 2019}}\n*{{Cite web|url=https://www.rediff.com/movies/review/review-zid-is-more-idiotic-than-erotic/20141128.htm|title=Review: Zid is more idiotic than erotic|website=Rediff|access-date=2 May 2019}}\n*{{cite web|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/hindi/bollywood/news/Zid-trailer-crosses-million-hits-online/articleshow/45012775.cms|title=Zid trailer crosses million hits online|date=2 November 2014|publisher=[[The Times of India]]|accessdate=4 November 2014}}\n*{{Cite web|url=https://mumbaimirror.indiatimes.com/entertainment/bollywood/Film-review-Zid/articleshow/45312963.cms|title=Film review: Zid|last=Desai|first=Rahul DesaiRahul|last2=Nov 29|first2=Mumbai Mirror {{!}} Updated|website=Mumbai Mirror|language=en|access-date=23 October 2019|last3=2014|last4=Ist|first4=00:00}}\n*{{Cite web|url=https://www.dnaindia.com/entertainment/review-film-review-take-an-aspirin-before-watching-zid-2039242|title=Film Review: Take an aspirin before watching Zid|last=Durham|first=Bryan|date=28 November 2014|website=DNA India|language=en|a