 Funk]]\n|-\n|62 || \"[[Only Women Bleed]]\" || [[Alice Cooper]]\n|-\n|63 || \"[[Doctor's Orders (song)|Doctor's Orders]]\" || [[Carol Douglas]]\n|-\n|64 || \"[[Get Down Tonight]]\" || [[KC and the Sunshine Band]]\n|-\n|65 || \"One Man Woman/One Woman Man\" || [[Paul Anka]] & [[Odia Coates]]\n|-\n|66 || \"[[You Are So Beautiful]]\" || [[Joe Cocker]]\n|-\n|67 || \"[[Feel Like Makin' Love (Bad Company song)|Feel Like Makin' Love]]\" || [[Bad Company]]\n|-\n|68 || \"[[How Sweet It Is (To Be Loved by You)]]\" || [[James Taylor]]\n|-\n|69 || \"[[Dance with Me (Orleans song)|Dance with Me]]\" || [[Orleans (band)|Orleans]]\n|-\n|70 || \"[[Cut the Cake (song)|Cut the Cake]]\" || [[Average White Band]]\n|-\n|71 || \"[[Never Can Say Goodbye]]\" || [[Gloria Gaynor]]\n|-\n|72 || \"[[I Don't Like to Sleep Alone]]\" || [[Paul Anka]] & [[Odia Coates]]\n|-\n|73 || \"[[Morning Side of the Mountain]]\" || [[Donny Osmond|Donny]] & [[Marie Osmond]]\n|-\n|74 || \"[[Some Kind of Wonderful (Grand Funk Railroad song)|Some Kind of Wonderful]]\" || [[Grand Funk Railroad]]\n|-\n|75 || \"[[When Will I See You Again]]\" || [[The Three Degrees]]\n|-\n|76 || \"[[Get Down, Get Down (Get on the Floor)]]\" || [[Joe Simon (musician)|Joe Simon]]\n|-\n|77 || \"[[I'm Sorry (John Denver song)|I'm Sorry]]\" || [[John Denver]]\n|-\n|78 || \"[[Killer Queen]]\" || [[Queen (band)|Queen]]\n|-\n|79 || \"[[Shoeshine Boy]]\" || [[Eddie Kendricks]]\n|-\n|80 || \"[[Do It ('Til You're Satisfied)]]\" || [[B.T. Express]]\n|-\n|81 || \"[[Can't Get It Out of My Head]]\" || [[Electric Light Orchestra]]\n|-\n|82 || \"Sha-La-La (Make Me Happy)\" || [[Al Green]]\n|-\n|83 || \"[[Lonely People]]\" || [[America (band)|America]]\n|-\n|84 || \"[[You Got the Love (Rufus song)|You Got the Love]]\" || [[Rufus (band)|Rufus]]\n|-\n|85 || \"[[The Rockford Files (song)|The Rockford Files Theme]]\" || [[Mike Post]]\n|-\n|86 || \"[[It Only Takes a Minute]]\" || [[Tavares (group)|Tavares]]\n|-\n|87 || \"[[No No Song]]\" || [[Ringo Starr]]